added some css, user profile shows reviews made by user. testing added for new models. use can upload profile image

Added a searching functionality so users can search for a specific anime and see the reviews made about that anime and add one if they want to. Data is retrieved from anime rest api called Jikan. Added some more unit testing to the user profile and review model. I added some bootstrap to templates to increase user experience.

added edits to review fixtures. added review model changes. added new edit, delete and new review view functions and relevant tamplates. fixed issue where user could not create a profile and save it. fixed issue where the user could not register. added new tests for new features added.
